Author: Haselnussbomber
Name: HaselTweaks
Punchline: A collection of quality of life tweaks.
Changelog:
Commands

- Fixed: The rarity color of item links could have been incorrect depending on the UI theme (I misinterpreted the UIColor sheet).

Gear Set Grid

- Changed: The Id column now uses the colored, framed job icon, and the layout has been changed to place the icon above the Id.

Author: Haselnussbomber
Name: LeveHelper
Description: A little helper to check which Levequests have been completed and which are missing.
Changelog:
Last update made things worse, but I hope this time we got the gatherable items all categorized correctly. 

- Added: Hidden gatherables are now marked as hidden in the queue.
- Added: The plugin has been translated into German. I don't understand other languages, so if you want to translate it into French or Japanese (or any other language), pull requests are welcome.
- Changed: Queue steps now have indentation for better readability.

Author: Haselnussbomber
Name: MogMogCheck
Description: MogMogCheck is small plugin that lists items from the Moogle Treasure Trove (in German called Mog Mog Kollektion), their collection status and checkmarks to track how many tomestones are needed.
Punchline: A plugin to assist tracking Moogle Treasure Trove rewards
